rue">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促梅赛德斯-奔驰在汽车领域合作中发挥“积极”作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-active-role-by-mercedes-benz-auto-sector-co-operation-2024-09-27/</link><description>该机构周五表示，中国国家规划部门负责人在北京会见了梅赛德斯-奔驰管理委员会主席康林松。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-active-role-by-mercedes-benz-auto-sector-co-operation-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市飙升至2008年以来最佳单周，日元因日本领导地位押注而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-27/</link><description>在北京推出大规模刺激计划以重振经济之后，中国股市迎来了自 2008 年以来最好的一周，并帮助亚洲股市升至 2-1/2 年高点，而油价大幅下跌预示着全球通货紧缩的好兆头。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 02:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着日本领导人之争的升温，日元下跌；中国刺激措施提振市场情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-risk-sensitive-currencies-lifted-by-china-optimism-2024-09-27/</link><description>日元周五下跌，因投资者等待日本首相替换选举的结果，而中国的一系列刺激措施使风险敏感型货币保持高位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-risk-sensitive-currencies-lifted-by-china-optimism-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯周五会见中国外交部长王毅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-wang-yi-friday-2024-09-27/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将于周五在纽约会见中国外交部长王毅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-wang-yi-friday-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国工业利润今年遭遇最大降幅，加剧经济困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profit-growth-swings-back-decline-august-2024-09-27/</link><description>继 7 月份增长 4.1% 后，8 月份利润同比下降 17.8%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:44:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profit-growth-swings-back-decline-august-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>油价因供应前景走强而下跌，中国刺激措施限制了损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-fall-expectations-higher-supplies-hammer-market-sentiment-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五油价连续第三天下跌，本周有望下跌，因为投资者关注利比亚和更广泛的欧佩克+集团产量增加的预期，尽管最大进口国中国的新刺激措施限制了损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-fall-expectations-higher-supplies-hammer-market-sentiment-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚财长访问北京讨论贸易、投资和近期刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-china-agree-cooperate-further-investment-trade-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五，澳大利亚财长吉姆·查默斯(Jim Chalmers)在罕见地访问北京期间表示，澳大利亚和中国同意在投资、贸易和脱碳方面进一步合作，并赞扬了中国最近宣布的经济刺激计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 00:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-china-agree-cooperate-further-investment-trade-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出较晚的刺激措施以实现2024年增长目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-cuts-banks-reserve-requirement-ratio-by-50-bps-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国央行降低利率并向银行体系注入流动性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 00:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-cuts-banks-reserve-requirement-ratio-by-50-bps-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国股市飙升，创十年来最佳一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 21:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>高市和石破将争夺日本下一任首相</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-ldp-picks-new-leader-replace-outgoing-pm-kishida-2024-09-26/</link><description>日本执政党将在周五进行第二轮选举，以决定谁将接任首相，一名寻求成为日本首位女首相的候选人将与一名第五次参加领导竞选的退伍军人进行角逐。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 20:04:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-ldp-picks-new-leader-replace-outgoing-pm-kishida-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称中国核动力潜艇今年沉没</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-nuclear-powered-submarine-sank-earlier-this-year-us-official-says-2024-09-26/</link><description>Planet Labs 六月份发布的一系列卫星图像似乎显示了武昌造船厂的起重机，潜艇本来就停泊在那里。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 18:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-nuclear-powered-submarine-sank-earlier-this-year-us-official-says-2024-09-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>